{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/add-gaps-faster-with-grid-gap","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"css-grid","demoType":null,"title":"Povećajte razmake što je moguće više pomoću grid-gap","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p><code>grid-gap</code> je svojstvo skraćivanja za <code>grid-row-gap</code> i <code>grid-column-gap</code> iz dve prethodne funkcije koje su najlakše za korišćenje. Ako <code>grid-gap</code> ima jednu vrednost, stvoriće razmak između svih redova i svih kolona. Međutim, ako postoji dve vrednosti, koristiće prvu vrednost da postavi razmak između redova i drugu vrednost za kolone.</p>\n</section>","id":"5a9036ee38fddaf9a66b5d37","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Koristi <code>grid-gap</code> da kreiraš razmak <code>10px</code> između redova i razmak <code>20px</code> između kolona.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":"https://scrimba.com/p/pByETK/ca2qVtv","superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301118,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/add-gaps-faster-with-grid-gap"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<style>\r\n  .d1 {\r\n    background: LightSkyBlue;\r\n  }\r\n  .d2 {\r\n    background: LightSalmon;\r\n  }\r\n  .d3 {\r\n    background: PaleTurquoise;\r\n  }\r\n  .d4 {\r\n    background: LightPink;\r\n  }\r\n  .d5 {\r\n    background: PaleGreen;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .container {\r\n    font-size: 40px;\r\n    min-height: 300px;\r\n    width: 100%;\r\n    background: LightGray;\r\n    display: grid;\r\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;\r\n    grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr 1fr;\r\n    /* Only change code below this line */\r\n\r\n    \r\n    /* Only change code above this line */\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n  <div class=\"d1\">1</div>\r\n  <div class=\"d2\">2</div>\r\n  <div class=\"d3\">3</div>\r\n  <div class=\"d4\">4</div>\r\n  <div class=\"d5\">5</div>\r\n</div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Klasa koja <code>container</code> treba imati svojstvo <code>grid-gap</code> koje stvara razmak od <code>10px</code> između redova i razmak od <code>20px</code> između kolona.</p>","testString":"assert.match(\r\n  code,\r\n  /.container\\s*?{[\\s\\S]*grid-gap\\s*?:\\s*?10px\\s+?20px\\s*?;[\\s\\S]*}/gi\r\n);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/#css-grid","dashedName":"add-gaps-faster-with-grid-gap","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"css-grid","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/use-grid-column-to-control-spacing","prevChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/create-a-row-gap-using-grid-row-gap","id":"5a9036ee38fddaf9a66b5d37","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<style>\r\n  .item3 {\r\n    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;\r\n    display: grid;\r\n  }\r\n</style>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/add-gaps-faster-with-grid-gap"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}